'''阿勒頗香皂'''是一种用[[橄欖油|橄榄油]]和[[碱液|碱液]]制成的手工[[肥皂|肥皂]]，並且含有[[月桂|月桂油]]。阿勒頗香皂的具體来源不明<ref name="botanicalgarden">{{cite web |last=Mosquin |first=Daniel |url=http://www.botanicalgarden.ubc.ca/potd/2008/03/laurus_nobilis.php |title=Laurus nobilis - Botany Photo of the Day |publisher=Botanicalgarden.ubc.ca |date=2008-03-26 |accessdate=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402231508/http://www.botanicalgarden.ubc.ca/potd/2008/03/laurus_nobilis.php |archive-date=2012-04-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="naturalcosmeticnews1">{{cite web |url=http://www.naturalcosmeticnews.com/new-products/aleppo-soap-the-true-natural-soap/ |title=Aleppo Soap, The True Natural Soap |publisher=Natural Cosmetic News |date= |accessdate=2012-07-09 |archive-date=2012-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902121425/http://www.naturalcosmeticnews.com/new-products/aleppo-soap-the-true-natural-soap/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。歷史上埃及女王[[克娄巴特拉七世|克娄巴特拉七世]]和叙利亚女王[[芝诺比娅|芝诺比娅]]均使用过它<ref name=guiliani>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rCTqOA2XebcC |title=Developing Markets for Agrobiodiversity: Securing Livelihoods in Dryland Areas |first=Alessandra |last=Giuliani |publisher=Earthscan |location=London |isbn=9781849770972 |date=2007 |access-date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2021-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211228173642/https://books.google.com/books?id=rCTqOA2XebcC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。人们普遍认为，肥皂的制作工艺源自[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]地区，而阿勒颇就是[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]的一个重要城市。

